Einstein Relationship Insights in ARC
Use the ARC Einstein Relationship Insights component to show account and contact record web recommendations.
View deeper relationship insights to build stronger customer relationships.
Available in Professional, Enterprise, and Unlimited editions.

To use this feature:
 Confirm the Financial Services Cloud package is installed.
 Configure person accounts with an additional person record object in the Einstein Relationship Insights setup page.
 Assign, enable, manage, and add Einstein Relationship Insights for the Actionable Relationship Center.

View web recommendations on the ARC Relationship Graph by selecting a record.
Take actions such as linking the recommendation to the record or creating a new record.
